name: Batonk!
blurb: Batonk! is the sound a robot makes when it runs into something. (and a delightful video game we want to make for you!)

rewards.reward: THANK YOU - A verbal thank you and an animated GIF of a Tunker singing the praises of backers.
CREDITED - Your name shall appear in the main crawl as a backer of the game. \r\n\r\nBONUS - Contribute $10 or more at this tier and we'll add a Tunker dancing next to your name.

THE GAME - A copy of the game on OUYA or PC. If more platforms are unlocked, you'll be able to choose your platform. Access to multiplayer prototypes. PLUS - Credited.\r\n\r\nBONUS - Contribute at least $20 at this tier and we'll send you some personalized animated GIFs of the Tunkers. Short of hatespeech and other atrocities, we'll have them say almost anything.
PLAY NOW, DARN IT! - A complete print-and-play kit to host your own live-action Batonk! party plus a short training video for the ref and the robots. PLUS Credited.

NAME A TUNKER - You may name one of the adorable robots that randomly appear in any match. Name them something appropriate, please. PLUS: Credited, Game\r\n\r\nBONUS - Contribute $75 or more and your Tunker's odds of appearing in any match go up 2x.

TUNKER TOYS - \r\nA limited-edition 3D-printed Tunker of your very own. The design will be special for the Kickstarter and will be HAND-PAINTED, individually-numbered, and feature markings or a style unique to YOUR Tunker. Plus Credited, the Game

HAPPY BIRTHDAY! MARRY ME! - A short APPROPRIATE message of your choosing will scroll across the scoreboard/marquees. Plus: Credited, Game\r\n\r\nBONUS - Contribute $150 or more and we'll double the chances your message appears in any given match and throw in a 4-pack of game codes.

CARD-CARRYING - Your own customized laser-engraved suitable-for-display membership card identifying you as a League Founder of the National Batonk! League OR as an Activist for the Council for the Ethical Treatment of Snarky Robots. PLUS Credited, Game.\r\n\r\nBONUS: DUAL ALLEGIANCE - Contribute at least $200 and get both.

ART - A PDF art book filled with the concept art, worldbuilding text (including the history of the League), and some making-of text and photos documenting the process of designing the game, producing the physical game, and then translating it digitally. Plus, Card-Carrying, Credited, Game\r\n\r\nBONUS - Yes, add $50 to get the DUAL ALLEGIANCE bonus.

ART AND SOUND - Everything from the Art tier plus a digital DRM-free download of the soundtrack from the game including a special commentary/Q&A track with the designers and composer.\r\n\r\nBONUS: Contribute $750 or more and get the DELUXE making-of including all the sketches and things we were too embarrassed to put in the regular making-of because they're bad or (knowing us, NSFW).

COSTUME - You suggest one of the Theme Days and vote on the concepts based on your suggestion that come back from the concept artists. You'll be credited in a fun way in the art credits. PLUS a four-pack of game downloads and the Card-carrying and Art and Sound tier rewards.

THE ART OF TUNKERS - A high quality suitable-for-display 8" one-of-a-kind maquette of a Tunker. Painted and customized by our friends in the designer toy community. Special credits featuring your name next to your custom Tunker. PLUS Game, Name a Tunker, Card-Carrying, Happy Birthday, Marry Me, Art and Sound.

THE CUP - Name the championship cup after you, or something you like. PLUS very special credits, a 5-pack of download codes to spread to your friends like Robot Father Christmas, your own marquee message, Art and Sound, and your own Named Tunker.

YOU ARE THE STADIUM - In real sports, some bigshot or company gets the field named after them So you can be that bighsot! We name the Batonk! stadium after you!  Most specialest credits, a special ID card designating your status as League Sponsor Supreme, name 2 of the Tunkers, specify up to 5 marquee messages, get the art and sound rewards, pick a Theme Day, and get 10 download codes (kickstarter limit) to hand out like the most excellent person you most definitely are. Plus, probably you just earned our love for life.
